---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
README to Translate to and from different languages available on translate.google.com using Selenium Web Driver for Firefox
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

================================
Install the selenium web driver:
-> pip install -U selenium
================================

================================================================================================
Download the latest version of geckodriver from: https://github.com/mozilla/geckodriver/releases
Extract and paste the driver in the '/usr/bin' or '/usr/local/bin' directory.
================================================================================================

========
Command:
-> python translate.py <input_file_name> <output_file_name>

The name of the input and output file must be according to the source language and target language which are available on Google Translate (translate.google.com).

For example:
Command to convert text in English to Hindi:
-> python translate.py english hindi

This command will take input data in English language which is present in the "english" file and the translated data will be stored in "hindi" file.